thread.title: AgentZero

author: AgentZero
title: AgentZero
text: I have been using Keepcalling for more than 5 years now and I have absolutely NO REASON to complain !!! Buying voice credits is easy, fast and simple. You can put an amount as low as 2$ so you're not FORCED to put a minimum amount that you might not need or use for a long time like other companies might do. I have never had any problem with them or a reason to complain. I HIGHLY RECOMMEND anyone to use them.
